name: Blood-Cell-Detection-TFOD-2.0
shortDescription: This project demonstrates the use of TensorFlow Object Detection API to automatically detect Red Blood Cells (RBCs), White Blood Cells (WBCs), and Platelets in each image taken via microscopic images.
longDescription: This project demonstrates the use of TensorFlow Object Detection API to automatically detect Red Blood Cells (RBCs), White Blood Cells (WBCs), and Platelets in each image taken via microscopic images.
